Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.01,0:01:49.51,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一切自將明了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.30,0:01:52.30,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夏娃
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.73,0:01:56.60,TEXT-CN(RED),,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夏娃
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.93,0:02:04.23,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這裡是…
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.98,0:02:17.38,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}終於醒了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.40,0:02:26.37,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你這隻家畜還真貪睡啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.51,0:02:28.47,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}家 家畜？
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.56,0:02:33.21,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你 你是誰
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.54,0:02:36.07,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還有 這裡是…
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.99,0:02:40.42,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼要把我帶…
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.75,0:02:44.31,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吵死了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.31,0:02:47.31,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}肥婆就不要唧唧歪歪了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.81,0:02:53.09,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了好了 畢竟她是被我們突然帶回來的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.09,0:02:55.32,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}難免會有些慌張嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.71,0:02:57.69,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對吧 小M貓
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.51,0:02:59.53,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我說
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.01,0:03:05.30,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你喜歡…弄痛嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.33,0:03:11.54,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 梓 別一上來就問這種問題嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.54,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先自我介紹一下吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.46,0:03:16.54,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以 容我們正式介紹一下自己吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.90,0:03:19.56,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我叫無神皓
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.92,0:03:22.02,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小M貓 請多指教
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.82,0:03:24.97,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是無神悠真
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.31,0:03:26.23,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}無神…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.75,0:03:28.95,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們是兄弟
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.18,0:03:30.76,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而他是…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.33,0:03:32.74,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我叫梓
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.44,0:03:38.44,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是琉輝
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.11,0:03:42.65,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這裡是我們住的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.65,0:03:45.85,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小M貓你今後也會住在這裡哦
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.58,0:03:47.66,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住在這裡？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.01,0:03:52.02,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不行 我要回去了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.26,0:03:54.13,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回去？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.54,0:04:01.30,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你想回逆卷家嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.74,0:04:07.55,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在那個家裡被那群吸血鬼當成玩物了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.55,0:04:08.33,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.37,0:04:14.50,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在他們的圈養下
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.50,0:04:18.84,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你已經打心底裡淪為被馴服的家畜了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.84,0:04:20.54,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我 我沒有
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.05,0:04:23.57,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但 但是
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.87,0:04:26.57,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們也是吸血鬼吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.12,0:04:30.33,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這樣的話 我待在這裡又有什麼區別
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.14,0:04:33.83,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別把我們和那些傢伙相提並論
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.04,0:04:38.14,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們最起碼有基本的是非觀
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.65,0:04:43.34,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你又有什麼證據值得我相信
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.57,0:04:48.81,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}煩死了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.58,0:04:54.10,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不相信又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.25,0:04:56.71,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒錯
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.22,0:04:59.29,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在這個計劃裡你的…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.10,0:05:03.19,TEXT-CN(RED),,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夏娃的血是不可或缺的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.59,0:05:05.88,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夏娃的血？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.48,0:05:09.46,TEXT-CN(RED),,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夏娃
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.98,0:05:14.17,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夏娃…是叫我？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.26,0:05:16.60,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.23,0:05:23.05,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你…就是…夏娃
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.05,0:05:26.09,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 不對 我不是夏娃
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.25,0:05:27.55,TEXT-CN(UP),,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哪來那麼多廢話
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.70,0:05:30.70,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你只要閉嘴聽話就行
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.88,0:05:46.34,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}擁有{\3c&H2A1CB6&\c&H000000&}夏娃{\r\blur2}之血的你
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.30,0:05:51.19,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一定能準確地找出來
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.76,0:05:55.02,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}誰是{\3c&H2A1CB6&\c&H000000&}亞當
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.82,0:05:57.96,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}亞當
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.82,0:06:05.76,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}從今天起 你將和我們一起住在這裡
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.35,0:06:08.28,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不管你如何掙扎
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.56,0:06:13.39,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要你還是夏娃 就必須遵守我們的規則
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.02,0:06:16.39,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你先在這裡冷靜一下
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.10,0:06:39.10,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可惡
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.90,0:06:42.46,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哪兒都找不到平胸那傢伙
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.59,0:06:47.32,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是 小賤人究竟跑哪兒去了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.88,0:06:51.16,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有點渴了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.06,0:06:54.85,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}昴你知道嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.03,0:06:57.22,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我怎麼會知道
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.70,0:07:04.06,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}身為食物竟敢隨便亂跑 不可饒恕
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.50,0:07:06.09,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}她到底去哪兒了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.83,0:07:08.49,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}隨她去吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.36,0:07:11.61,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}早晚會回來的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.79,0:07:20.01,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但願如此
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.03,0:08:07.22,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在哪兒
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.11,0:08:11.69,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出口在哪兒
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.72,0:08:52.72,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}居然想要逃走
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.14,0:08:56.05,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}果真是缺乏教養的家畜
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.20,0:08:58.66,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今晚你就睡這裡
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.05,0:09:04.06,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你想逃可以
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.06,0:09:07.19,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但在付諸行動後 等待你的就只有懲罰了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.16,0:09:09.94,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你最好做好心理準備
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.05,0:09:18.53,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你這副表情 是想讓我同情你嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.53,0:09:20.18,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}才 才不是
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.59,0:09:24.36,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真不巧 吸血鬼可不吃這一套
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.19,0:09:41.47,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.56,0:09:50.31,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夏娃…嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.22,0:09:58.45,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們夢寐以求的獨特存在
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.64,0:10:01.34,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}竟然是你這種平凡的女人
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.63,0:10:09.13,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 這也是為了達成目的
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.18,0:10:18.30,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 不要
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.04,0:10:26.78,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原來如此
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.25,0:10:29.90,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這就是夏娃的血
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.85,0:10:33.93,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住手
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.54,0:11:10.36,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要是那位大人的要求
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.70,0:11:15.42,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們將{\3c&H2A1CB6&\c&H000000&}永遠渴求你的鮮血
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.91,0:12:22.76,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你想逃就逃吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.63,0:12:25.99,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等待著你的只有懲罰
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.80,0:12:29.35,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的血是一切的源頭
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.76,0:12:30.76,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夏娃
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.96,0:12:34.33,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是夏娃的話 一定會為我們指明方向吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.78,0:12:37.88,TEXT-CN(RED),,0,0,0,,{\blur2}洗淨你身上的汙痕
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.11,0:12:39.53,TEXT-CN(RED),,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刻上屬於我的印記
